public class ColumnViewPort
extends com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.widget.Viewport

This is the ViewPort for EasyGWT. An instance of this class gives you access to the entire framework behind EasyGWT. Holds and adds all Panel elements to GWT's RootPanel.

Author:
Alfredo Quiroga-Villamil
